  <description><![CDATA[<p>The family-run Seiler's Vintage Hotel (ex Alfa Soleil) is a traditional building close to the center of <a data-udi="umb://document/08db820246524b63b3bfadde3a69e4f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/08db820246524b63b3bfadde3a69e4f2}" title="Kandersteg">Kandersteg</a> village. There's a huge variety of walking trails on the doorstep, and with the railway station just a five-minute walk away you'll have easy public transport access to the wider region too.</p>
<h2>Great for families</h2>
<p>The hotel is loved by guests for its relaxed atmosphere and guest-house feel. Each of the 30 bedrooms is individually styled and has a unique personality. Balcony rooms have spectacular mountain views, and some can fit additional bunk beds - a great option for families. There's a cosy piano lounge that's great for quiet evenings in, billiards, and a play area too.</p>
<h2>Pretty gardens, and a relaxing pool &amp; spa</h2>
<p>The hotel is surrounded by beautiful mountain scenery and lovely gardens. The mini wellness center has an indoor swimming pool that's perfect for a refreshing dip at the end of a day in the mountains. There's also a steam room, mountain water showers, a Finnish sauna, and a relaxation area.</p>]]></description>
